inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let timeGrain=5m;
let dataset=requests
    // additional filters can be applied here
    | where client_Type != "Browser"
    | where (iif(itemType == "request", (column_ifexists('customDimensions', '')["system_SystemName"] == "account-management"), (itemType == "request" and column_ifexists("id", operation_ParentId) in ((requests
        | where customDimensions["system_SystemName"] == "account-management"
        | distinct id))) 
        or (itemType != "request" and operation_ParentId in ((requests
        | where customDimensions["system_SystemName"] == "account-management"
        | distinct id)))));
dataset
// change 'operation_Name' on the below line to segment by a different property
| summarize Count=sumif(itemCount, (iif(itemType == "request", (column_ifexists('customDimensions', '')["system_SystemName"] == "account-management"), (itemType == "request" and column_ifexists("id", operation_ParentId) in ((requests
    | where customDimensions["system_SystemName"] == "account-management"
    | distinct id))) 
    or (itemType != "request" and operation_ParentId in ((requests
    | where customDimensions["system_SystemName"] == "account-management"
    | distinct id)))))), Avg = avg(duration), Percentiles_95 = percentiles(duration, 95)
    by operation_Name
// calculate duration percentiles and count for all requests (overall)
| union(dataset
    | summarize Count=sumif(itemCount, (iif(itemType == "request", (column_ifexists('customDimensions', '')["system_SystemName"] == "account-management"), (itemType == "request" and column_ifexists("id", operation_ParentId) in ((requests
        | where customDimensions["system_SystemName"] == "account-management"
        | distinct id))) 
        or (itemType != "request" and operation_ParentId in ((requests
        | where customDimensions["system_SystemName"] == "account-management"
        | distinct id)))))), Avg = avg(duration), Percentiles_95 = percentiles(duration, 95)
    | extend operation_Name="Overall")
| order by Percentiles_95
| where Percentiles_95 > 1000

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let systemName = "account-management";
let timeFrame = 28d;
let topRequests=requests
| where timestamp > ago(timeFrame)
| where customDimensions["KubernetesNamespace"] == systemName
| where operation_Name != ""
| summarize Count = count() by operation_Name
| order by Count
| top 6 by Count
| project operation_Name
;
requests
| where operation_Name in (topRequests)
| where timestamp > ago(timeFrame)
| where customDimensions["KubernetesNamespace"] == systemName
| summarize Duration=percentiles(duration, 95, 99) by operation_Name, bin(timestamp, 7d)
| render timechart

content.PartTitle: Most Called Requests Duration Over Time (95th percentile)

inputs.name: Query
Query
inputs.value:
let endDateTime = now();
let startDateTime = ago(12h);
let trendBinSize = 30m;
let capacityCounterName = 'memoryLimitBytes';
let usageCounterName = 'memoryRssBytes';
let containerWebApiSystemInternal = "integration-management-webapi-private" ;
Perf
| where InstanceName contains containerWebApiSystemInternal
| where TimeGenerated < endDateTime
| where TimeGenerated >= startDateTime
| where ObjectName == 'K8SContainer'
| where CounterName == capacityCounterName
| summarize LimitValue = max(CounterValue) by InstanceName, CounterName, bin(TimeGenerated, trendBinSize)
| project InstanceName, CapacityStartTime = TimeGenerated, CapacityEndTime = TimeGenerated + trendBinSize, LimitValue
| join (
  Perf
  | where InstanceName contains containerWebApiSystemInternal
  | where TimeGenerated < endDateTime + trendBinSize
  | where TimeGenerated >= startDateTime - trendBinSize
  | where ObjectName == 'K8SContainer'
  | where CounterName == usageCounterName
  | project InstanceName, UsageValue = CounterValue, TimeGenerated
) on InstanceName
| project InstanceName, TimeGenerated, UsagePercent = UsageValue * 100.0 / LimitValue
| summarize AggregatedValue = avg(UsagePercent) by bin(TimeGenerated, trendBinSize), InstanceName
| render timechart
